OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunshine best in the early to
OL,6,Fmid-morning, tending to turn hazy as
OL,7,Fhigher cloud increases into the
OL,8,Fafternoon. Most staying dry but a few
OL,9,Flight showers may crop up. Southeast
OL,10,Fwinds strong.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud thickening to bring
OL,13,Fperiods of rain, with some heavier
OL,14,Foutbreaks late evening and during the
OL,15,Fearly hours of Wednesday, before
OL,16,Fturning patchy towards dawn. Strong
OL,17,Fsoutherly winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
