OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FMainly cloudy with
OL,6,Foccasional showers, most of these
OL,7,Feither side of noon. Southerly winds
OL,8,Foccasionally fresh across Shetland.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FPeriods of rain Thursday, clearing to
OL,12,Fshowers late in the day. Friday mainly
OL,13,Fdry, occasionally bright, but gales
OL,14,Fand rain expected late in day.
OL,15,FSaturday windy and occasionally wet.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
